data.description: Welcome this fully renovated Single Family home! Step inside this charming 4 well-sized bedrooms, 2-bathroom home that boasts a renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the serene ambiance of the outdoors on your private deck. Plus, if you're a fan of swimming, you'll love the 12x24 pool, just steps away, fulfilling your desire for a refreshing dip during warm days. The home features new windows, ensuring ample natural light throughout the day, and well-maintained screen doors that add to the overall charm. For your convenience, the basement provides an additional living space, perfect for a family room or home office. Walk up attic easily accessible for storage or other purposes. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a renovated, detached home with all the modern amenities you desire. Conveniently located! Close to restaurants, shops, parks, schools and public transportation.
